   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-accepting-a" mid="150" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Heraldry Scholar Bailey is saying things he always says.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="149"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR>People think that Ancient Magic or Divine Magic are the answers to the world's problems.<BR>But... that simply isn't true.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-accepting-b" mid="152" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="151"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR>The actual <FONT color=#a82424>desire to learn</FONT> is what enables people to understand the ways of the world.<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Knowledge</FONT> what truly makes everything clear.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-accepting-c" mid="154" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Ok..So what do you want me to help you in?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="153"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR>Therefore, we should never stop having <FONT color=#a82424>questions about all things in the world</FONT>.<BR>Do you understand, my dear adventurer?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-accepting-acceptted" mid="156" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, ask away.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="155"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR>I actually had a question for a while now...<BR>I'm asking because I see that <FONT color=#a82424>Cloth Chaser</FONT> title on you, but...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-1" image="QM_GoblinGreen.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-a" mid="162" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Umm... I g-guess?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="160"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR>As you know, Goblins truly practice the ways of nature with their whole being by wearing just a single <FONT color=#a82424>Loincloth</FONT>.<BR>They are quite the frugal race.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-b" mid="164" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>So?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="163"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey${action:Talk}<BR>However, they also carry <FONT color=#a82424>Old Headbands</FONT> and <FONT color=#a82424>Protection Talismans</FONT>.<BR>I've seen plenty of adventurers who kill Goblins just to sell those items.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-b" image="QN_Npc_Scholar_Baily.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-c" mid="166" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>... (Heraldry Scholar Bailey sounds quite serious.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="165"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR>Those Goblins...<FONT color=#7e12d2> (Heraldry Scholar Bailey stares at you with a serious face.)</FONT><BR><FONT color=#a82424>Where</FONT> do you think they keep those items...?!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-d" mid="168" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Somewhere you can't see...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-e" mid="169" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I doubt they have pockets.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="167"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR>I thought you would know because you've been collecting <FONT color=#a82424>Loincloths</FONT>.<BR>Does it have a... pocket? How are the pockets attached?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-d" image="QM_GoblinGreen.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-f" mid="173" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You are going write a report?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="170"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR>Somewhere you can't see?! A hidden pocket on such a small cloth! That's truly shocking.<BR>Amazing... I should do a detailed research and write up a report.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-e" image="QM_GoblinGreen.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-f" mid="174" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Why... why would you research something like that?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="171"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR>No pockets? If not inside pockets, where do they hide their items?! How?!<BR>Hmm... truly mysterious indeed. I will have to go see how it looks like under the cloth.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-g" mid="176" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>That's true... (So what "way" is that?)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="175"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR>The greed for truth and knowledge is what truly reveals the way of the world.<BR>I mentioned it before, but how can one find out about anything if one does not question?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-g" image="QN_Npc_Scholar_Baily.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="179"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR>Thank you for the information. I'll be asking you many more things in the future. I have so much questions about the world that I want the answer to. Hahaha.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(It appears that you've gotten closer with Heraldry Scholar Bailey.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
